  * refactor: deduplicate code in `screen.rs` (https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/1453)
  * chore(dependencies): update  `clap`: `3.1.18` -> `3.2.2` (https://github.com/zellij-org/zellij/pull/1496)
